Show HN: What you think of this Excel to database add-in? [Video]
text:
I have been developing easy way for non-IT people to upload data from Excel to database to be able to use the data in BI system and for example no-code app builders and similar. I'm interested to hear what people think of this solution?

Add-in is not yet in any marketplace so I recorded video (https://youtu.be/Rxmvx6AMFK0) which shows how uploading, appending and overwriting data works.

What you think? Could this be useful?

Ask HN: How does DST time change impact your global remote team?
text:
I just woke up where two different remote teams have requested meeting time changes to adjust for DST changes.

I am in the US and they are in Asia.

A few of these meetings are recurring.

As a result, I’d be losing an hour of sleep.

How do people do this? Shine an axe and keep your calendar entry unchanged?

Move it to accommodate people’s local time zones?
